            <title>日约会 App 开发商指年轻人失去浪漫想像，推出 AI 女友提升拍拖意欲</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/dating-app-develop-ai-girlfriend/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dating-app-develop-ai-girlfriend</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/dating-app-develop-ai-girlfriend/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 13:00:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tapple]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220716</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年发达国家少子化问题愈来愈严重，日本有研究显示 2050 起或会出现全国人口减少，因此推出官方约会应用程式，以 <span class="s1">AI </span>技术为日本市民扩阔配范围。然而日本其中一个大型交友 App 开发商 Tapple 则认为真正问题是年轻人失去浪漫想像，因此推出了<span class="s1"> AI </span>女友「Koi Sura AI」，重塑年轻人对拍拖的期望。</p><p>「Koi Sura AI」是日本东京 Tapple, Inc. 开发的手机游戏，其名字亦非常有巧思，「 koi suru 」的意思是「恋爱」，「AI」则既是人工智能的缩写，也是日语中「爱」的意思，同时亦是女性的名字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220748" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ka2-694x339.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ka2-694x339.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ka2.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://soranews24.com/2024/01/18/japans-biggest-dating-app-says-young-people-not-interested-in-romance-creates-ai-girlfriend-app/">soranews24</a></p><p>「Koi Sura AI」是一款约会模拟游戏，游戏主题环绕与一位名叫 Ai 的 22 岁女性沟通。开发商盼用家可以「增加日本的浪漫度」，缓解日本少子化问题。由「玩约会游戏」到「现实生活中结婚生子」的跨度似乎很漫长，但开发商表示希望透过「Koi Suru AI」向用户呈现一种真实感觉的关系，从而激发用户在现实建立浪漫关系。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220747" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ka3-694x547.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="547" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ka3-694x547.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ka3.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://soranews24.com/2024/01/18/japans-biggest-dating-app-says-young-people-not-interested-in-romance-creates-ai-girlfriend-app/">soranews24</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://japantoday.com/category/national/feature-ai-plays-cupid-as-japanese-authorities-try-to-boost-marriage-rate">Japan Today</a>、<a href="https://soranews24.com/2024/01/18/japans-biggest-dating-app-says-young-people-not-interested-in-romance-creates-ai-girlfriend-app/">Sora News 24</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/22/chatgpt-with-voice/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】ChatGPT 语音对话，听得明广东话 + 直接语音回答</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/reddit-signs-ai-content-licensing-deal-ahead-of-ipo/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Reddit 出售用户内容训练 AI　估计每年收入价值 6 千万美元</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/microsoft-openai-google-and-others-agree-to-combat-election-related-deepfakes/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">科技企业担心 AI 影响美国大选　20 间公司达成共识进行监管</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/dating-app-develop-ai-girlfriend/ai/">日约会 App 开发商指年轻人失去浪漫想像，推出 AI 女友提升拍拖意欲</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
